name: Jabra Elite 65t - True wireless earphones with mic - in-ear - Bluetooth | Dell USA
description: Jabra Elite 65t is engineered for the best true wireless calls and music experience. Unique four-microphone technology gives you effective wind-noise reduction* on calls, and our advanced 6mm speakers give you Jabra HearThrough – delivering, at the touch of a button, external ambient noise into the earbuds for audio awareness of what's around you.
